description.narrative: The Project endorses the objectives of the National Strategic Plan. Its development objectives are to: improve parentingeducation and support programs; (ii) improve monitoring of children's development, the screening of household level risks, and therisk mitigation and early intervention systems, (iii) enhance the quality of early childhood schools and care facilities; and (iv)strengthen ealy childhood organizations and institutions.
